 create them.  \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Under this initiative, our companies will measure what they are doing and communicate this to the public. They also will learn from one another about what works.  \par \par \uc2 Mr. Pearlstein said "old-fashioned government regulation" is the fair and reliable way to a better world. Sometimes. But regulation often is just the floor of what can and needs to be accomplished. Regulation levels the field and seeks to prevent harm. Sustainable innovation, on the other hand, seeks to provide solutions.  \par \par \uc2 We don't see sustainable growth as "do-goodism." Sustainability is about meeting the needs of the present without compromising the ability of future generations to meet their own needs.  \par \par \uc2 CHARLES O. HOLLIDAY JR.  \par \par \uc2 Wilmington, Del.  \par \par \uc2 The writer, chairman and chief executive of DuPont, is also chairman of the Business Roundtable's \b \highlight22\uc2 Environment\b0 \highlight\uc2 , Technology and the Economy Task Force.  \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b CT\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 http