a is to use chemical pesticides and fertilizers to protect tea bushes from nature's mood swings. But over time, the buildup of pesticides such as atrazine (the same compound that produces dual-sex frogs) has been found to be harmful to ecosystems, not to mention to the health of tea pickers and tea drinkers.  \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Do gasoline prices accurately capture the cost of our military efforts to secure petroleum supplies? Do the prices of SUVs or even lawnmowers reflect the cost of stepped-up carbon dioxide emissions?  \par \par \uc2 It would be idealistic, and unproductive, to envision a society where every cost is accurately reflected in the prices consumers pay. But we shouldn't give businesses a free ride and say that we only expect them to give us cheap goods without considering the long-term impact of their decisions on the \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2 , their workers and their customers.  \par \par \uc2 SETH GOLDMAN  \par \par \uc2 President and TeaEO  \par \par \uc2 Honest Tea Inc.  \par \par \uc2 Bethesda  \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b CT\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnu