lpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Paul Deighton expected that when he became chief executive of London 2012, someone would present him with a book telling him how sponsorship worked and how to value domestic sponsorship rights for the Olympic Games. \par \par \uc2 "It doesn't exist," the 50- year-old former Goldman Sachs partner said with the look of a man who has spent the past six months writing it himself. \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 "We really set about constructing the case from first principles. I went back to what I knew, which was investment banking transactions. \par \par \uc2 "We are trying to create the same analytical rigour around making the case for investment that you would make if you were a Fidelity fund manager looking at buying one of Goldman Sachs' IPOs." \par \par \uc2 His commercial team, headed by Chris Townsend, former Transport for London commercial director, researched previous games and concluded one thing: start as early as you can. \par \par \uc2 The 2004 Athens Olympics was late not just in construction, the commercial team concluded, but in getting its sponsorship programme ready. "As a principle, people have probably not paid very much (for games domestic sponsorship) and under-utilised it," said Mr Deighton. \par \par \uc2 "If you start early, if you're really thoughtful about this, you can pay a bit more but your own return as the sponsor can double or triple." \par \par \uc2 Locog, the organising committee of London 2012, wants its main domestic sponsors on board in 2007, giving them "spike" points in the course of their six-year sponsorship - rights of association with Britain's competing teams in the Beijing Olympics in 2008 and the Vancouver winter games in 2010. \par \par \uc2 "Your rights are back in the UK, but clearly at the time of Beijing and Vancouver, there is huge Olympic value," said Mr Deighton. \par \par \uc2 The sales pitch is built around a methodology that Mr Townsend claims is nothing less than rewriting the book on sports marketing. "A number of companies expressed difficulty in evaluating sponsorship agreements in other areas," he said. \par \par \uc2 The aim is for companies to take the methodology away and work out for themselves the benefit of being a 2012 main sponsor to the bottom line. \par \par \uc2 "So if you're a bank launching a credit card branded with Olympic rings . . . they know very specifically how many customers they will recruit at the end of that programme and the lifetime value of those customers," said Mr Townsend. \par \par \uc2 Would-be sponsors are taken through Locog's potential benefits - bigger market share, \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2 , improved productivity and absenteeism levels, association with national pride and enhanced brand equity and financial performance. \par \par \uc2 Signing up as exclusive sponsors buys them options to "activate" other 2012 sponsorship opportunities - in education, \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2 , sports participation and volunteering. \par \par \uc2 Companies are given a range for the value of a 2012 sponsorship in their sector based on precedent from previous Olympics - but not Athens - and adjusted for inflation, population, economy and size of sector in the UK. Non-Olympic sports deals, such as Emirates' Pounds 100m sponsorship of Arsenal FC, is added to the equation. \par \par \uc2 Locog uses previous examples, such as Olympic credit card launches, to map how the directly quantifiable benefits of new customers and internal company benefits can be assessed in terms of new products, productivity and other areas. \par \par \uc2 Mr Deighton said the uplift from less quantifiable benefits was best left to companies to determine. \par \par \uc2 "We are trying to create a methodology which is intellectually clear and honest," he said. \par \par \uc2 "Our job is to get them excited about the Olympic model, that this is of a different order."  \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b RF\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 20061114L106.078\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b CO\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 gldmns : \uc2 The Goldman Sachs Group Incorporated\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b IN\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustrigh