t\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Companies are being urged by investors to put social and environmental responsibility at the heart of their decision-making, rather than treating the issues as public relations "add-ons". \par \par \uc2 The Association of British Insurers, which represents investors owning one-fifth of the UK stock market, yesterday called on companies to attach greater importanceto non-financial issues and give investors more useful information about them. \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Corporate responsibility activists have sought to push social and environmental factors toward the mainstream for several years, with only limited success. \par \par \uc2 The government's last-minute decision to abolish mandatory reports on non-financial performance - known as operating and financial reviews - dealta blow to the movementlast year. \par \par \uc2 But in a position paper yesterday, the ABI stressed the importance of managing and acknowledging publicly the social, environmental and ethical risks that companies face. \par \par \uc2 Peter Montagnon, ABI director of investment affairs, said: "Where you can see a company is on top of these risks, people will be more confident in the quality of its earnings." \par \par \uc2 The corporate responsibility movement has broadened from sector-specific concerns, such as the environmental impact of oil and mining groups, to deal with a wider range of issues affecting all businesses and their owners. \par \par \uc2 "\b \highlight22\uc2 Corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2  reports are essentially public relations. \par \par \uc2 "We're saying some of this stuff belongs in the annual report proper," said MrMontagnon. "It should be something the board is looking at." \par \par \uc2 The ABI specifically wants companies to publish statements - known as "narrative reports" - on factors that could have an impact on future performance. \par \par \uc2 "We find these corporate responsibility reports are not normally very useful be-cause they're too long. They don't distil the essence. That's what boards need to do," Mr Montagnon said.  \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b RF\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 20061130L103.082\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b NS\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 ccsr : \uc2 Corporate Social Responsibility | ccat : \uc2 Corporate/Industrial News | genv : \uc2 Environmental News | gcat : \uc2 Political/General News | ncat : \uc2 Content Types | nfact : \uc2 Factiva Filters | nfcpex : \uc2 FC&E Executive News Filter\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clv